title: BEAUTIFUL FULLY FURNISHED IN BRICKELL HOUSE!
posting_body: ['Fully furnished and ready for you to call home.', 'This spacious 1/1 offers complete bay views from all rooms with an extra long balcony to sit and indulge in all the beauty Brickell Bay has to offer.', 'Building amenities include two pools, hot tub, sauna/treatment rooms, gym, club room, movie theater, resident lounge, and complimentary coffee.', 'One parking space is included and all utilities are included in rent.', 'Walking distance to Mary Brickell Village, Brickell City Centre, Metromover, and MetroRail.', 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!TEXT :', 'show contact info']
